{"tid":797620,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★外媒報道 華為次季出貨量超Apple　篤定全球手機二哥","createTime":"2018-08-28T15:43:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-24T01:55:28.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"210c050ea84500ca01f865a518bc197041649c39","tid":797620,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T15:43:30.000Z","msg":"外媒報道，繼早前國際市場調查機構IDC公布，今年第2季，國產智能手機一哥華為踢走蘋果公司(Apple Inc.)，成為全球「手機二哥」後，今日再有研究機構Gartner發報告稱，第2季的智能手機出貨量，華為出貨達4,985萬部，市佔率晉升第二位，市佔率大增38.6%，期內蘋果公司iPhone出貨量僅升0.9%、至4,472萬部。<br />\n<br />\n全球智能手機商第1位依舊是三星，市佔率19.3%，但出貨量郤較去年同期減少過千萬部，而華為及蘋果的市佔率分別為13.3%及11.9%；排名第4位的是小米(01810)，出貨量達3,282萬部，市佔率8.8%；同是國產品牌的OPPO則排名第5位，出貨量2,851萬部，市佔率7.6%。<br />\n<br />\n報告認為，華為次季出貨量的大幅增長跟其手機持續創新，以及市場已遍布全球70個國家和地區有關，而蘋果公司iPhone X的銷售較以往早出現放緩迹象亦有關係。不過，蘋果公司已準備今年秋季推出更多顏色選擇的3款新機，以應付一眾國產手機品牌的挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180828/bkn-20180828225905918-0828_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20180828%2Fbkn-20180828225905918-0828_00842_001.html&d=2r2ZVseub07168zjZY9EKG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=533199c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180828/bkn-20180828225905918-0828_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"6ecc6ba2cf080ad71ec07dcca9635e6c73edae61","tid":797620,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T15:43:41.000Z","msg":"apple rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f5af56c62718313be37c85310df9601da83a4ee","tid":797620,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T15:44:50.000Z","msg":"[img][/img]"},{"pid":"2f20678fa5e84325afe26bede8d66d42de633d9c","tid":797620,"uid":2572,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score"